# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Order delivery (server-side only — NOT exposed to the browser).
#
# The Google Apps Script Web App URL that receives orders and appends them
# to your Google Sheet. Used by app/api/order/route.ts.
#
# Local dev:  copy this file to ".env.local" and paste your URL below.
# Production: set this same variable in your host's dashboard
#             (Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GOOGLE_SHEET_WEBHOOK_URL=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Telegram order backup (free, optional — server-side only).
#
# Every order is also posted as a message to your Telegram chat, so you
# have a permanent, searchable record on your phone. Set BOTH values to
# enable it; leave blank to disable. The order is considered saved if the
# Sheet OR Telegram succeeds, so this also acts as a failover.
#
# TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN  – from @BotFather (e.g. 7123456:AAH...).
# TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID    – your chat/group id (from @userinfobot). For a group,
#                       add your bot to it; group ids are negative (e.g. -100...).
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN=
TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID=
